    {
      "id": "sybil_20_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_20",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle offers a refined driving experience and a professional aesthetic. Meticulously maintained to ensure mechanical integrity, it features a well-preserved interior and a robust powertrain. This selection represents an ideal acquisition for the discerning driver seeking a sophisticated balance of performance, comfort, and enduring value.",
