      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_22_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_22",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a super reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a solid companion. It\u2019s in really nice shape, runs like a dream, and has been well-loved over the years. It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home\u2014feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
